name: Dogecast
description: Inspired by the viral tweet that captured the essence of meme culture, $DOGECAST is here to amplify the spirit of DOGE on the blockchain. Born from a hilarious moment on Twitter, $DOGECAST is all about sharing laughs, spreading good vibes, and connecting the community with a token that doesn’t take itself too seriously. With DOGE’s iconic legacy and a fresh twist, $DOGECAST is ready to transmit fun across the crypto world—one meme at a time! 🐕🚀
